title: Jordy Smith vs Kelly Slater at the Rip Curl Pro
description:
The final day of the Portugal event saw Jordy make the final against one of
his heroes-Kelly Slater. There weren't many good waves to be had in the
dying swell but Jord's still pulled a superman air out of his bag of tricks.
Unfortunately he couldn't find a decent second wave and Kelly, 16 years
older than Jordy, took the honours. The pair are now the only guys in
contention for the 2010 world title with two events to go...
